{"tid":1580863,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"開左個IG介紹撐港餐廳，推埋比外國遊客參考","createTime":"2019-09-19T09:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T16:43:12.000Z","uid":35777,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"48c215108c79f3b03b08b9e94eadc0892757e272","tid":1580863,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac出post<br />\n<br />\n自從發現左手足整合嘅黃藍地圖之後，過去兩個禮拜差唔多日日都幫襯黃店。但係發現用個map搵餐廳嘅時候無得以食物菜色/總類search，所以開左個ig介紹下呢d餐廳有咩食，等大家可以睇相揀食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我記得之前有個post係分享小店食物，但搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫襯良心餐廳記得影相投稿，分享下邊度有咩好食，齊齊制裁呢d餐廳，做到佢地無停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外IG嘅post我特登譯埋英文，想將d餐廳推埋比黎香港想支持個運動嘅外國朋友，等佢地咪再食美心富臨呢d賣港集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【終極整合】黃藍商戶地圖 (持續更新中)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/XDHrEJQM5fRn2Bxh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FXDHrEJQM5fRn2Bxh8&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=dcdaaa73\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/XDHrEJQM5fRn2Bxh8</a><br />\nIg: standwithhkfood"},{"pid":"a37ca131d9522a01e2b9a8f4696c38bc13cdca5a","tid":1580863,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=1221636f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"570d16cf1e588fafc4829882abb32e731c0f57ab","tid":1580863,"uid":112915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a7f19f0cdb3ba7d8fec1e14ff7e517b5fec5de","tid":1580863,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc0452650c8b2b6e90c5d37e80e80d44e5582593","tid":1580863,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家有好野分享記得dm我，或者post喺度都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c6364f22e83d0e1e71049fb5f9194d3c959f77","tid":1580863,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"79410946f707aca40dde98b8147d06c4e099cd27","tid":1580863,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係有心既 都係做好事 但幫手推下啲行動post"},{"pid":"04580452efa691dbe5e910064edfa80505753242","tid":1580863,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19e682a0c3ef351a79e577ff21fa86eec23ad24","tid":1580863,"uid":35777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79410946f707aca40dde98b8147d06c4e099cd27","tid":1580863,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係有心既 都係做好事 但幫手推下啲行動post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"有呀，喺Twitter推緊全球反chinazi遊行<br />\n#globalantichinazismmarch<br />\n戰線一條都不能